{"content": "I need to multiply 210 \u00d7 5a0 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n210\u2081\u2081 to base 10:\n- 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- 2\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 0\n- 242 + 11 + 0 = 253\u2081\u2080\n\n5a0\u2081\u2081 to base 10:\n- 5\u00d711\u00b2 + 10\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- 5\u00d7121 + 10\u00d711 + 0\n- 605 + 110 + 0 = 715\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n253 \u00d7 715 = 180,895\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert back to base 11**\n180,895 \u00f7 11 = 16,445 R 0\n16,445 \u00f7 11 = 1,495 R 0\n1,495 \u00f7 11 = 135 R 10 (a)\n135 \u00f7 11 = 12 R 3\n12 \u00f7 11 = 1 R 1\n1 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 1\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 113a00\n\n113a00", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 365, "completion_tokens": 352}